    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“You’ll die,” says Meru matter-of-factly. He doesn’t threaten you but merely states the obvious. “Glabrio and his rats will die too, so you can’t save them. You can only save yourself.”</npc_text>
